  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK715">
<l>naṉṟeṉ ṟavaṟṟuḷḷu naṉṟē mutuvaruṇ </l>
<l>muntu kiḷavāc ceṟivu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The modesty by which one does not rush forward and speak in (an assembly of) superiors is the best among all (one's) good qualities.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
